This expresses the successive rounds of organization and investment in a startup.  The information is organized into Dashboards.  The Dashboards include deal points and links to forms of documents.  For both Seed and Series A rounds, the reference is to a "Binder" of documents.  <br>
This establishes a name space of, for instance:  SeriesA.TermSheet. ....  The name space is used to instantiate each of the documents by referencing the Dashboard and specifying an appropriate key.

